The,Venmo,API,is,made,up,of,two,different,public,APIs,The,Payment,Links,API,provides,a,simple,method,for,sending,invoices,or,suggested,payments,via,any,medium,Email,SMS,Facebook,Twitter,Payment,links,have,optional,parameters,and,are,constructed,by,adding,these,parameters,to,the,base,URL,The,Receipts,API,allows,every,Venmo,user,to,send,receipt,data,for,payments,they,receive,to,a,third,party,webservice,By,default,users,get,receipts,via,Email,and,SMS,but,the,Receipts,API,provides,a,simple,method,for,automating,followup,actions,to,payments,like,collecting,a,postal,address,for,fulfillment,or,automating,digital,fulfillment,via,email